\subsubsection parameters ROS parameters

Reads and maintains the following parameters on the ROS server

- \b "~cluster_tolerance" : \b [double] tolerate_value min: 0.0, default: 0.1, max: 20.0
- \b "~min_cluster_size" : \b [int] min_cluster min: 0, default: 2, max: 200
- \b "~max_cluster_size" : \b [int] max_cluster min: 0, default: 1000, max: 2000

